application_details.scheme_name: Britannia Point / The Tower (Brown & Root House)

description: Demolition of the existing multistorey car park, conversion of and alterations / extensions to the tower block; erection of a new building (combined) to provide 218 flats, 2 retail (A1) units, a new public library facility (629 square metres), Class B1 business/office adaptable space 923 sq.m, a café/bar (102 square metres), creation of public open space together with car and cycle parking provision and landscaping. Application under S73 for amendments to conditions, attached to planning permission reference 03/P0202 to enable a phased development
